01:19:48,412 --> 01:19:50,291
-How you feeling?
-Feeling good.

882
01:19:50,314 --> 01:19:53,298
What were you knuckleheads
doing out there, causing a ruckus?

883
01:19:57,854 --> 01:20:00,336
You're wearing my favorite color!

884
01:20:00,389 --> 01:20:02,531
I said I'd come and I was gonna be
dressed like you today.

885
01:20:02,592 --> 01:20:03,628
It's nice.

886
01:20:03,694 --> 01:20:06,735
Kenny put me onto this kind of T-shirt,
these kind of shirts.

887
01:20:06,930 --> 01:20:09,242
I would never have worn this
if it wasn't for Kenny.

888
01:20:11,234 --> 01:20:13,147
-How you doing? Good with you.
-What up, man?

889
01:20:13,202 --> 01:20:14,546
-How are you?
-I'm good.

890
01:20:14,604 --> 01:20:15,606
What up?

891
01:20:26,349 --> 01:20:28,957
This is an honor.
it's an honor to perform with you guys.

892
01:20:29,018 --> 01:20:30,521
While we're doing all this,

893
01:20:30,620 --> 01:20:32,602
I want you to
keep your voice as still as you can.

894
01:20:32,688 --> 01:20:35,102
We're still not out of the woods yet.
We got a big show tonight.

895
01:20:35,158 --> 01:20:36,194
So, no talking.

896
01:20:36,459 --> 01:20:38,634
Wow. You're on the floor.

897
01:20:39,995 --> 01:20:42,979
-Oh, my God!
-You are a saint! You are a saint!

