01:21:11,793 --> 01:21:14,868
Wait till you hit the stage.
When you got that in your system...

907
01:21:14,930 --> 01:21:16,274
When you get to
the second phase of the show...

908
01:21:16,331 --> 01:21:17,811
I'm 16. I always have energy.

909
01:21:17,865 --> 01:21:20,610
Okay. But you won't be 16 forever.

910
01:21:24,672 --> 01:21:26,847
Group hug, fellas.

