912
01:21:29,544 --> 01:21:33,894
You're family, the little man in our lives.
I'm sure I speak for all of us when I say

913
01:21:33,948 --> 01:21:35,053
we're proud right now.

914
01:21:37,318 --> 01:21:38,765
-Love you.
-Love you, too, man.

915
01:21:38,820 --> 01:21:41,063
Should he kill this now in front of you
so you know he drank it?

916
01:21:41,122 --> 01:21:43,628
Please.

917
01:21:43,691 --> 01:21:45,000
Finish it, man. Finish it.

