01:21:46,661 --> 01:21:49,439
Come on. it's not that bad, dude.

920
01:21:50,431 --> 01:21:53,074
Ten minutes! Ten minutes!

921
01:21:58,505 --> 01:22:03,516
I was once chilling in my room,
watching TM just in a regular place.

922
01:22:03,644 --> 01:22:08,530
And now I'm in this big world,
living my dream and doing what I love.

923
01:22:10,617 --> 01:22:13,260
It's just crazy how it all came around.

924
01:22:27,234 --> 01:22:28,613
Let's go!

925
01:22:28,669 --> 01:22:30,240
Bring him down.

926
01:22:31,171 --> 01:22:32,207
Got to roll.

927
01:22:41,815 --> 01:22:44,958
New York City.
Are you having a good time so far?

928
01:22:45,018 --> 01:22:47,398
It's the My World Tour!

